"msg":"撤回！撤回！"},{"pid":"0f86642e818e151f12bf4f136016accc11ef3d3b","tid":1222702,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:35:45.000Z","msg":"對我母校好失望，屌你老母乜撚野叫做「本校不代表任何立場」？"},{"pid":"a6d3625ca25ed45554be6e99bdb0749676f23ab0","tid":1222702,"uid":83052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:37:31.000Z","msg":"好多人係IG見到暫緩就鬆懈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以多啲人提出，暫緩唔係撤回，共軍用嘅招「敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追」<br />\n群眾一退就危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74add61e9d7dfd62128ed98c59e3da90f1d93aac","tid":1222702,"uid":65384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"有我母校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝校長"}]}